Take this endpoint:

```java
@Endpoint(id = "test")
@Component
public class TestEndpoint {
    @ReadOperation
    public Mono<String> sessionsForUsername(String username) {
        return Mono.just("test");
    }
}
```

When I execute `curl http://localhost:8080/actuator/test`, I get

```
